snippet.title: The Gristmill Trailer
snippet.description:
April trailer for The Gristmill. The Gristmill is a tactical strategy card game with light rougelike and deckbuilding elements set within a fantasy universe from Several People.

Several People is made up of:
Robert Bailey
Ashwin Ganapathiraju
Tetyana Kolomiyets
Samantha Levey
Jason Rose
Trevor Walden
